Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:06.10,Italics,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Furuya Hotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.04,Italics,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Today is my first day of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:11.20,Italics,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have an awesome brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:12.88,Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1)}My Brother's Girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:17.63,Italics,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,He's the class representative.\NHis job is to take care of his whole class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:20.51,Italics,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad he's so serious\Nthat he can't get a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.47,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:24.61,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Furuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:26.22,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.67,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,M-Minagawa-san. Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.06,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:31.98,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Ho-Hotaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:33.24,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:34.64,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:36.90,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks for taking care of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.37,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're so polite. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.87,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just {\i1}being{\i0} polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.76,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:44.94,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is she just a classmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:45.68,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you close?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.32,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have more girl friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:48.92,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Hotaru, that's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.82,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You love your brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:52.63,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:53.41,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:55.21,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, she's really attached to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:57.19,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that? She's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:00.22,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you to my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.48,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:03.20,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:05.18,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,What is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.75,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'm wrong, but to be really sure,\Nyou two aren't dating, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.73,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.46,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,We're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:12.94,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:13.88,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:15.07,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.32,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru, you're hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:21.96,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed to him, but he hasn't\Ngiven me an answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.49,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,So not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.16,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, she's trolling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.62,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,The answer's obvious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.91,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.12,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:33.69,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and reject her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.30,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll hurt her if you lead her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.46,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hotaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.20,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Furuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.75,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Reject me if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.58,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:46.81,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:50.28,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.55,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.07,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:58.08,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell I'm worried for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.60,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's just toying with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.99,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only get hurt if you go out with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.30,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.87,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not thinking of dating her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:07.62,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Have I just been rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.07,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.52,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.71,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:15.76,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Minagawa-san, I can't go out\Nwith you without thinking it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.78,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if we did, we'd have\Nto think about marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.74,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,and finances, and then kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.64,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You've been {\i1}that{\i0} serious about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.93,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.33,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.74,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's {\i1}always{\i0} serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.82,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.54,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,He really is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.98,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.78,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll give you some more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.65,Default,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:43.26,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be rooting for me, right, Hotaru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.34,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.66,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.18,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.50,Default,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll adore both of you together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.35,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I freaking hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.25,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't really anything\Nthat I'm drawn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.30,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interests or hobbies\Nthat keep me engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.79,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm a boring person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:05.72,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,But is anyone really interested\Nby what they say they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.27,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.93,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you'd like stars and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.39,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna join the astronomy club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.82,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.96,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.27,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.41,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, at least hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:19.70,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.79,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.90,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Have you chosen a club yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.74,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:27.28,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Then want to join me in watching\Nan orchestra of stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.18,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I mess that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.04,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.37,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Is it any fun watching the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.50,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.29,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.67,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get bored just watching them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.05,sign_7377_117_Sweat___________,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sweat\NSweat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.05,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.12,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else interesting about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:44.72,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.22,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Club members are popular. Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.72,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,So far, 100% of its members have hooked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.10,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.26,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.27,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really like stars\Nthat much, do you, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.60,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you in the astronomy club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:02.19,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Well, y'know, I like the vibe of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.41,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.11,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,How many other members are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.24,sign_7377_117_Sweat___________,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sweat\NSweat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.47,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.72,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.65,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't interested\Nin any other clubs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.34,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.50,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you a story\Nthat'll make you like stars, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:17.42,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.05,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.38,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,There's a star called Spica\Nsomewhere around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.88,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like one big star,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:28.62,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,but it's actually two stars\Nspinning around and pulling each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.75,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:33.06,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Two stars help each other\Nand become one big light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.21,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that philosophical?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.08,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.30,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.02,Default,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.67,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,That's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:41.07,sign_8114_135_I_ripped_off_Sen,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I ripped off \NSenpai's story...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.08,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.48,sign_8183_137_I_feel_like_he_t,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like he taught \Nme all kinds of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:46.49,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.41,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I had delicious takoyaki while watching Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.86,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,My senpai, who just graduated, was, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.95,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,"Martians look like octopus, don't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.47,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,So I made takoyaki as we watched Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:00.71,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,But Senpai stared at Mars the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.20,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,so I scarfed them all down by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.80,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't even about stars anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:14.31,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,She must really love the astronomy club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.85,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be absorbed\Nby something, the way she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.56,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kaga-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.40,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.06,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't really anything\Nthat I'm drawn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.01,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,I was sick of being such a boring person,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.42,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd been looking for something to like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.56,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what I've been looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.91,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:44.13,Italics,Kaga,0000,0000,0000,,But I felt the need\Nto see more of this smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:49.76,Default,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.89,Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.39,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Kamine sits next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.00,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,She avoids me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.79,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.68,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:09.74,sign_10170_162_Contact,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1600)}Contact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.15,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kamine, aren't you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.03,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I-I will, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.18,Italics,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,She won't even look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.98,Italics,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.37,Italics,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.95,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gouda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.25,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.91,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.54,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,I just lost a contact lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.28,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:29.98,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.80,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care not to step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.72,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.93,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me look for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.32,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.47,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:39.15,Italics,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she doesn't really hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.24,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Do you lose your contacts often?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.08,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.25,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,Like when I wipe away my sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.48,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:53.16,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Kamine, is there something\Nthat you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:00.00,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to answer to your wishes\Nto the best of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.91,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,So you can tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.04,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,You must already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.29,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,considering what you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.28,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what you might mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.44,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.07,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how you lent me your notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:21.68,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,when I was having a hard time seeing\Nin class because of my eyesight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.63,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.69,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:30.19,Italics,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.47,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.40,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.19,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find your contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.26,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,If I can at least find it for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.31,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,Gouda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.22,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.82,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,What's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.26,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,My answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.96,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:59.26,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to tell you how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.15,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking me to own up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.08,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.40,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.27,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,All right, if that'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.28,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.78,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.83,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, it's not easy for me\Nto understand how girls feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.18,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:26.29,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surely cause you more trouble\Nif I were to be near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.46,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll accept me nonetheless, then please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.50,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I found your contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.97,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:46.23,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you'll go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.77,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.94,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that was implied\Nby what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.34,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.90,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Kamine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.07,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Am I crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:03.73,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:08.34,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't confessed properly, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:09.69,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.38,Default,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something you\Nwant to tell me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.76,Default,Kamine,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:28.39,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:30.50,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.57,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,No umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.47,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun is in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.27,sign_15234_233_Rain,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.28,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really talked to him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.49,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.37,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:42.49,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:50.04,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I felt bad, so we walked\Nhome together part way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:51.80,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.07,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,It must be embarrassing,\Nwalking home with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.79,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.50,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Not with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.80,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he means no one would\Nsuspect anything if it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.22,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.02,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoulder's getting wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.71,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.89,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Come closer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:13.86,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.45,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,A little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:21.10,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aren't you embarrassed\Ndoing this with a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:21.98,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.28,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,No one's looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:27.98,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I mean, what if your\Ncrush saw you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.28,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.63,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you grinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.98,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.32,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone confessed to you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.82,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,No one would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.96,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Hypothetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.59,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}if{\i0} someone confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.60,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd turn them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.72,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:53.48,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be something wrong\Nwith anyone who'd confess to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:56.22,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cute. I'm gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.57,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.28,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,You're always helping people clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.78,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,and you take care of the pupfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.11,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.85,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.66,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the bus here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.46,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you about to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.55,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.23,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:24.30,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.47,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Dating, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.46,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.87,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.43,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:33.75,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.79,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.80,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.75,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd finish saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:48.07,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, um, Takano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:51.23,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,I-I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.58,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.58,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to cheer me up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.52,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.33,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.05,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.50,Default,Sugawara,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is my stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.89,Default,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.14,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:22.98,Italics,Takano,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll bake him cookies\Nas thanks for the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Short-Distance Relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.03,Next_Ep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}Short-Distance Relationships
